[
  {
    "text": "I used to think the whole purpose of life was pursuing happiness.",
    "uid": "bce027440b39a29c",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 12.59,
    "end": 17.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Everyone said the path to happiness was success,",
    "uid": "fba7ce33e3170f5b",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 18.59,
    "end": 21.59
  },
  {
    "text": "so I searched for that ideal job,",
    "uid": "9c211fd0cbbdacf8",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 21.59,
    "end": 24.59
  },
  {
    "text": "that perfect boyfriend, that beautiful apartment.",
    "uid": "23469638c87d0e1b",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 24.59,
    "end": 27.59
  },
  {
    "text": "But instead of ever feeling fulfilled,",
    "uid": "84091307b0f3c839",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 28.59,
    "end": 31.59
  },
  {
    "text": "I felt anxious and adrift.",
    "uid": "060fead137d5cd7b",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 31.59,
    "end": 34.59
  },
  {
    "text": "And I wasn't alone, my friends, they struggled with this too.",
    "uid": "2622baa2c7c51784",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 34.59,
    "end": 38.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Eventually, I decided to go to graduate school",
    "uid": "23b226f2d66bf092",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 39.59,
    "end": 42.59
  },
  {
    "text": "for positive psychology to learn what truly makes people happy.",
    "uid": "b1794504c36e6163",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 42.59,
    "end": 47.59
  },
  {
    "text": "But what I discovered they're changed my life.",
    "uid": "14c8fce81b1207f0",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 47.59,
    "end": 50.59
  },
  {
    "text": "The data showed that chasing happiness can make people unhappy.",
    "uid": "53732145733cc57e",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 51.59,
    "end": 55.59
  },
  {
    "text": "And what really struck me was this,",
    "uid": "e44d85309d792d9f",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 56.59,
    "end": 59.59
  },
  {
    "text": "the suicide rate has been rising around the world",
    "uid": "a4d7279c18a1d6f0",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 60.59,
    "end": 63.59
  },
  {
    "text": "and it recently reached a 30 year high in America.",
    "uid": "d1f99a9bfd1f9959",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 63.59,
    "end": 66.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Even though life is getting objectively better",
    "uid": "ce49665aadcc10b7",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 66.59,
    "end": 69.59
  },
  {
    "text": "by nearly every conceivable standard,",
    "uid": "8778018d34448715",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 69.59,
    "end": 72.59
  },
  {
    "text": "more people feel hopeless, depressed, and alone.",
    "uid": "edcd59fd481facf2",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 72.59,
    "end": 76.59
  },
  {
    "text": "There's an emptiness, knocking away at people,",
    "uid": "4ae53345eaefada1",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 77.59,
    "end": 80.59
  },
  {
    "text": "and you don't have to be clinically depressed to feel it.",
    "uid": "dc315804b8526c45",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 80.59,
    "end": 82.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Sooner or later, I think we all wonder,",
    "uid": "110d586ba4c2cc6a",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 83.59,
    "end": 86.59
  },
  {
    "text": "is this, all there is.",
    "uid": "d72b3178327a6dcd",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 87.59,
    "end": 89.59
  },
  {
    "text": "And according to the research, what predicts this despair",
    "uid": "4492fdb6e46a6419",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 90.59,
    "end": 93.59
  },
  {
    "text": "is not a lack of happiness.",
    "uid": "5be56074bd05e225",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 93.59,
    "end": 95.59
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a lack of something else,",
    "uid": "14c506fcdbbc2f01",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 95.59,
    "end": 97.59
  },
  {
    "text": "a lack of having meaning in life.",
    "uid": "ac9c788ac1422cad",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 98.59,
    "end": 101.59
  },
  {
    "text": "But that raised some questions for me,",
    "uid": "9e992a4963d50b94",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 102.59,
    "end": 104.59
  },
  {
    "text": "is there more to life than being happy?",
    "uid": "c5348d606c1e8faa",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 105.59,
    "end": 107.59
  },
  {
    "text": "And what's the difference between being happy",
    "uid": "e95730178b896ae8",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 108.59,
    "end": 110.59
  },
  {
    "text": "and having meaning in life?",
    "uid": "98831572c8085a3a",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 110.59,
    "end": 112.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Many psychologists define happiness",
    "uid": "c0e4ae21abcdffc0",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 114.59,
    "end": 116.59
  },
  {
    "text": "as a state of comfort and ease, feeling good in the moment.",
    "uid": "761dbb460640efd9",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 116.59,
    "end": 120.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Meaning though is deeper.",
    "uid": "3307152553b7bbb1",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 121.59,
    "end": 123.59
  },
  {
    "text": "The renowned psychologist Martin Seligman",
    "uid": "97a6df17e3b30cfc",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 124.59,
    "end": 126.59
  },
  {
    "text": "says meaning comes from belonging to and serving something beyond yourself,",
    "uid": "356d0b5a78955db0",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 126.59,
    "end": 130.59
  },
  {
    "text": "and from developing the best within you.",
    "uid": "2eda8147a5e10869",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 131.59,
    "end": 133.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Our culture is obsessed with happiness,",
    "uid": "099db65a5bef7c2d",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 135.59,
    "end": 137.59
  },
  {
    "text": "but I came to see that seeking meaning is the morph of filling path.",
    "uid": "1095800469355618",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 138.59,
    "end": 141.59
  },
  {
    "text": "And the study showed that people who have meaning in life,",
    "uid": "b2a86662ff881d43",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 142.59,
    "end": 144.59
  },
  {
    "text": "they're more resilient, they do better in school and at work,",
    "uid": "685e332323e61bdf",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 145.59,
    "end": 148.59
  },
  {
    "text": "and they even live longer.",
    "uid": "5e0c462bfdee710a",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 148.59,
    "end": 150.59
  },
  {
    "text": "So this all made me wonder,",
    "uid": "a24d7396cba7eaff",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 151.59,
    "end": 153.59
  },
  {
    "text": "how can we each live more meaningfully?",
    "uid": "3c38c8ca2c850426",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 153.59,
    "end": 155.59
  },
  {
    "text": "To find out, I spent five years interviewing hundreds of people",
    "uid": "f1ea3f3cac3b73da",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 157.59,
    "end": 160.59
  },
  {
    "text": "and reading through thousands of pages of psychology,",
    "uid": "44a034c1d25bc579",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 161.59,
    "end": 163.59
  },
  {
    "text": "neuroscience, and philosophy.",
    "uid": "5b2b88e5d9b278c7",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 164.59,
    "end": 166.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Bringing it all together,",
    "uid": "068c7a9147c62af9",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 167.59,
    "end": 168.59
  },
  {
    "text": "I found that there are what I call four pillars of a meaningful life.",
    "uid": "34de5b9e83380963",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 169.59,
    "end": 173.59
  },
  {
    "text": "And we can each create lives of meaning",
    "uid": "4e49a32a7c1b9cd3",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 174.59,
    "end": 176.59
  },
  {
    "text": "by building some or all of these pillars in our lives.",
    "uid": "bae9a7eafd437a14",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 176.59,
    "end": 179.59
  },
  {
    "text": "The first pillar is belonging.",
    "uid": "07a84d4fda6023e3",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 180.59,
    "end": 182.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Belonging comes from being in relationships where you're valued for who you are intrinsically,",
    "uid": "57dd74b03dbd2467",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 183.59,
    "end": 188.59
  },
  {
    "text": "and where you value others as well.",
    "uid": "e693e8f422c76d9e",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 189.59,
    "end": 191.59
  },
  {
    "text": "But some groups and relationships deliver a cheap form of belonging.",
    "uid": "c06b1ac10e3d5ad8",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 192.59,
    "end": 196.59
  },
  {
    "text": "You're valued for what you believe, for who you hate, not for who you are.",
    "uid": "1a9cc41b8b73e198",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 197.59,
    "end": 201.59
  },
  {
    "text": "True belonging springs from love.",
    "uid": "43f61883eb3a7b58",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 202.59,
    "end": 204.59
  },
  {
    "text": "It lives in moments among individuals,",
    "uid": "183132ef4d179430",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 204.59,
    "end": 207.59
  },
  {
    "text": "and it's a choice you can choose to cultivate belonging with others.",
    "uid": "a4c50d10401b359b",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 208.59,
    "end": 211.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's an example.",
    "uid": "6239378cef27d0ca",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 212.59,
    "end": 213.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Each morning, my friend Jonathan buys a newspaper from the same street vendor in New York.",
    "uid": "b5f9e8ccc8254d6f",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 214.59,
    "end": 219.59
  },
  {
    "text": "They don't just conduct a transaction, though, they take a moment to slow down,",
    "uid": "b8a58852754786b1",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 220.59,
    "end": 224.59
  },
  {
    "text": "talk, and treat each other like humans.",
    "uid": "8ba3b43700a3b694",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 225.59,
    "end": 227.59
  },
  {
    "text": "But one time, Jonathan didn't have the right change.",
    "uid": "ef4f201bb2dff36e",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 228.59,
    "end": 230.59
  },
  {
    "text": "And the vendor said, don't worry about it.",
    "uid": "9ab10472671a1cff",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 230.59,
    "end": 233.59
  },
  {
    "text": "But Jonathan insisted on paying.",
    "uid": "d28a5966f6f610de",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 234.59,
    "end": 236.59
  },
  {
    "text": "So he went to the store and bought something he didn't need to make change.",
    "uid": "0987e720d94d4fe6",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 237.59,
    "end": 240.59
  },
  {
    "text": "But when he gave the money to the vendor, the vendor drew back.",
    "uid": "bcc687cb4b618907",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 241.59,
    "end": 245.59
  },
  {
    "text": "He was hurt.",
    "uid": "bd3c6abefb7b5d36",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 246.59,
    "end": 247.59
  },
  {
    "text": "He was trying to do something kind, but Jonathan had rejected him.",
    "uid": "8a9f624e091093a8",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 248.59,
    "end": 251.59
  },
  {
    "text": "I think we all reject people in small ways like this without realizing it, I do.",
    "uid": "2600203fdcf91fb8",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 253.59,
    "end": 258.59
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll walk by someone I know and barely acknowledge them.",
    "uid": "3d598145591298bb",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 258.59,
    "end": 261.59
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll check my phone when someone's talking to me.",
    "uid": "36bdeb234e862680",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 262.59,
    "end": 264.59
  },
  {
    "text": "These acts devalue others. They make them feel invisible and unworthy.",
    "uid": "ef05507d77c62979",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 265.59,
    "end": 269.59
  },
  {
    "text": "But when you lead with love, you create a bond that lifts each of you up.",
    "uid": "c72930f049003601",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 270.59,
    "end": 274.59
  },
  {
    "text": "For many people, belonging is the most essential source of meaning.",
    "uid": "3cf75766cf0d8916",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 275.59,
    "end": 279.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Those bonds to family and friends.",
    "uid": "ec3424666764b7c4",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 280.59,
    "end": 282.59
  },
  {
    "text": "For others, the key to meaning is the second pillar.",
    "uid": "6c662647abcd8caa",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 283.59,
    "end": 285.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, finding your purpose is not the same thing as finding that job that makes you happy.",
    "uid": "85478b4263fdc2a2",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 287.59,
    "end": 292.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Purpose is less about what you want than about what you give.",
    "uid": "901494763369cda4",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 293.59,
    "end": 295.59
  },
  {
    "text": "A hospital custodian told me her purpose is healing sick people.",
    "uid": "c41d37b392c2bc93",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 296.59,
    "end": 300.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Many parents tell me, my purpose is raising my children.",
    "uid": "c47c4e8040261b83",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 301.59,
    "end": 304.59
  },
  {
    "text": "The key to purpose is using your strengths to serve others.",
    "uid": "98ec36145ca072a0",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 305.59,
    "end": 308.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Of course, for many of us, that happens through work.",
    "uid": "87c0876291f2d412",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 309.59,
    "end": 312.59
  },
  {
    "text": "That's how we contribute and feel needed.",
    "uid": "9ad448afba460e9c",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 312.59,
    "end": 315.59
  },
  {
    "text": "But that also means that issues like disengagement at work, unemployment, low labor force participation.",
    "uid": "0204eb56774d7500",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 316.59,
    "end": 323.59
  },
  {
    "text": "These are just economic problems, their existential ones too.",
    "uid": "8cc7e598a426e582",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 324.59,
    "end": 327.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Without something worthwhile to do, people flounder.",
    "uid": "f3b5bf1a751f8974",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 328.59,
    "end": 331.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Of course, you don't have to find purpose at work, but Purpose gives you something to live for.",
    "uid": "2f0f9f088e70a734",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 332.59,
    "end": 337.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Something to live for, some why that drives you forward.",
    "uid": "1f7bf9dcdbf5de9c",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 337.59,
    "end": 340.59
  },
  {
    "text": "The third pillar of meaning is also about stepping beyond yourself, but in a completely different way.",
    "uid": "1b2a86f70fcfc258",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 343.26,
    "end": 347.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Transcendence states are those rare moments when you're lifted above the hustle and bustle of daily life.",
    "uid": "1bb2367f766ef333",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 350.26,
    "end": 355.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Your sense of self fades away and you feel connected to a higher reality.",
    "uid": "b418b018938ce215",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 356.26,
    "end": 359.26
  },
  {
    "text": "For one person I talked to, Transcendence came from seeing art.",
    "uid": "342130a384024f8e",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 360.26,
    "end": 364.26
  },
  {
    "text": "For another person, it was at church.",
    "uid": "2944351cedd260a2",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 365.26,
    "end": 367.26
  },
  {
    "text": "For me, I'm a writer, and it happens through writing.",
    "uid": "5a9ec7fb1a2d9ed6",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 367.26,
    "end": 370.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Sometimes I get so in the zone that I lose all sense of time and place.",
    "uid": "e13016a86965405e",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 371.26,
    "end": 375.26
  },
  {
    "text": "And these Transcendent experiences can change you.",
    "uid": "236d15bbbf681e64",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 376.26,
    "end": 379.26
  },
  {
    "text": "One study had students look up at 200 feet tall you could lift histories for one minute.",
    "uid": "b73fb9f693cc5a6c",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 380.26,
    "end": 385.26
  },
  {
    "text": "But afterwards, they felt less self-centered and they even behaved more generously when given the chance to help someone.",
    "uid": "9cf9cbd7d877c945",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 386.26,
    "end": 391.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Belonging, Purpose, Transcendence.",
    "uid": "e4b84b247339ccd1",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 391.26,
    "end": 396.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, the fourth pillar of meaning I found tends to surprise people.",
    "uid": "a81723c3bab9b791",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 397.26,
    "end": 402.26
  },
  {
    "text": "The fourth pillar is storytelling.",
    "uid": "6b615404320ff567",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 403.26,
    "end": 405.26
  },
  {
    "text": "The story you tell yourself about yourself.",
    "uid": "b309cd445488f774",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 406.26,
    "end": 408.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Creating a narrative from the events of your life brings clarity.",
    "uid": "9d60b600590ac588",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 409.26,
    "end": 413.26
  },
  {
    "text": "It helps you understand how you became you.",
    "uid": "95e494ea11b80926",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 414.26,
    "end": 416.26
  },
  {
    "text": "But we don't always realize that where the authors of our stories and can change the way we're telling them.",
    "uid": "9f6a21577367e59b",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 416.26,
    "end": 421.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Your life isn't just a list of events.",
    "uid": "ae65575891811089",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 422.26,
    "end": 424.26
  },
  {
    "text": "You can edit, interpret, and re-tell your story even as you're constrained by the facts.",
    "uid": "e573087a9c58c240",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 425.26,
    "end": 430.26
  },
  {
    "text": "I met a young man named Emma K.",
    "uid": "380d8e05b355ba08",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 431.26,
    "end": 433.26
  },
  {
    "text": "who'd been paralyzed playing football.",
    "uid": "d69be14212be0d4c",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 434.26,
    "end": 435.26
  },
  {
    "text": "After his injury, Emma K. told himself,",
    "uid": "11585e258b643123",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 436.26,
    "end": 438.26
  },
  {
    "text": "My life was great playing football.",
    "uid": "bdbd8e685a4dfdda",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 439.26,
    "end": 441.26
  },
  {
    "text": "But now, look at me.",
    "uid": "3b8e51a6b46e6d41",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 442.26,
    "end": 443.26
  },
  {
    "text": "People who tell stories like this, my life was good, now it's bad.",
    "uid": "289b920aff93f2dd",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 443.26,
    "end": 449.54
  },
  {
    "text": "They tend to be more anxious and depressed.",
    "uid": "02f0284e3202d4e5",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 450.54,
    "end": 452.54
  },
  {
    "text": "And that was Emma K. for a while.",
    "uid": "82844ea8ba62660d",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 453.54,
    "end": 455.54
  },
  {
    "text": "But with time, he started to weave a different story.",
    "uid": "edd470a534e423bf",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 456.54,
    "end": 459.54
  },
  {
    "text": "His new story was, before my injury, my life was purposeless.",
    "uid": "f0316974cf8f02a1",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 460.54,
    "end": 464.54
  },
  {
    "text": "I partied a lot and was pretty selfish guy.",
    "uid": "7f756da1650c5129",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 465.54,
    "end": 467.54
  },
  {
    "text": "But my injury made me realize I could be a better man.",
    "uid": "58e58377298a80cd",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 468.54,
    "end": 471.54
  },
  {
    "text": "That added to his story changed Emma K. life.",
    "uid": "beac07180ee02964",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 471.54,
    "end": 475.54
  },
  {
    "text": "After telling the new story to himself, Emma K. started mentoring kids,",
    "uid": "e3e2e6c51d22ea49",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 476.54,
    "end": 480.54
  },
  {
    "text": "and he discovered what his purpose was, serving others.",
    "uid": "2c64fa1f76967367",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 481.54,
    "end": 484.54
  },
  {
    "text": "The psychologist, Dan McAdams, called this a redemptive story,",
    "uid": "84944e3573f73879",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 485.54,
    "end": 488.54
  },
  {
    "text": "where the bad is redeemed by the good.",
    "uid": "b6c0b7ddf169c49f",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 489.54,
    "end": 490.54
  },
  {
    "text": "People leading meaningful lives, he's found.",
    "uid": "b592761d01028085",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 491.54,
    "end": 493.54
  },
  {
    "text": "They tend to tell stories about their lives defined by redemption, growth, and love.",
    "uid": "44fd3d8debbc6723",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 494.54,
    "end": 498.54
  },
  {
    "text": "But what makes people change their stories?",
    "uid": "da4277d8c44a122f",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 498.54,
    "end": 501.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Some people get help from a therapist, but you can do it on your own too,",
    "uid": "9775af0be297c487",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 502.54,
    "end": 506.54
  },
  {
    "text": "just by reflecting on your life thoughtfully.",
    "uid": "00ed4129f8101eee",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 507.54,
    "end": 509.54
  },
  {
    "text": "How you're defining experiences shaped you, what you lost, what you gained.",
    "uid": "f88b1f9a357658ee",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 510.54,
    "end": 513.54
  },
  {
    "text": "That's what Emma K. did.",
    "uid": "2c78ce39a55a2107",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 514.54,
    "end": 515.54
  },
  {
    "text": "You won't change your story overnight. It could take years and be painful.",
    "uid": "6489bed85a366496",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 516.54,
    "end": 520.54
  },
  {
    "text": "After all, we've all suffered and we all struggle.",
    "uid": "6355eba8dc22773c",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 521.54,
    "end": 523.54
  },
  {
    "text": "But embracing those painful memories can lead to new insights and wisdom.",
    "uid": "04ba1d231f1f9042",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 524.54,
    "end": 527.54
  },
  {
    "text": "To finding that good that sustains you.",
    "uid": "778248801bf96085",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 528.54,
    "end": 531.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Belonging, purpose, transcendence, storytelling.",
    "uid": "0a137e299b61cb99",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 534.42,
    "end": 538.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Those are the four killers of meaning.",
    "uid": "a7501055c73f12db",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 539.42,
    "end": 541.42
  },
  {
    "text": "When I was younger, I was lucky enough to be surrounded by all of the pillars.",
    "uid": "c978d4f2478ed57b",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 542.42,
    "end": 547.42
  },
  {
    "text": "My parents ran a Sufi meeting house from our home in Montreal.",
    "uid": "b0ffdd4aaefd9348",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 548.42,
    "end": 552.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Sufism is a spiritual practice associated with the whirling dervishes and the poet Rumi.",
    "uid": "e6855466f9dbbf0f",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 553.42,
    "end": 559.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Twice a week, Sufis would come to our home to meditate, drink,",
    "uid": "b7a5591d35e01656",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 561.42,
    "end": 565.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Persian tea and share stories. Their practice also involves serving all of creation through small acts of love,",
    "uid": "37b1b6fce243d77a",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 566.42,
    "end": 572.42
  },
  {
    "text": "which meant being kind even when people wronged you.",
    "uid": "65767cbc9d7dd73c",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 573.42,
    "end": 575.42
  },
  {
    "text": "But it gave them a purpose to reign in the ego.",
    "uid": "6010fe37006ed1ff",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 576.42,
    "end": 579.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Eventually, I left home for college and without the daily grounding of Sufism in my life,",
    "uid": "1af59748bf768b0b",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 581.42,
    "end": 586.42
  },
  {
    "text": "I felt unmoored and I started searching for those things that make life worth living.",
    "uid": "11ace708c2b5ebd9",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 586.42,
    "end": 591.42
  },
  {
    "text": "That's what set me on this journey.",
    "uid": "58fc0040a4b294cb",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 592.42,
    "end": 594.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Looking back, I now realized that the Sufi house had a real culture of meaning.",
    "uid": "abc598c90b16f4e6",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 595.42,
    "end": 599.42
  },
  {
    "text": "The pillars were part of the architecture and the presence of the pillars helped us all live more deeply.",
    "uid": "ec69a383ceb65696",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 600.42,
    "end": 605.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Of course, the same principle applies in other strong communities as well.",
    "uid": "ef73eaa7c27a53cc",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 606.42,
    "end": 610.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Good ones and bad ones.",
    "uid": "f5231c8eb99e81d8",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 611.42,
    "end": 613.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Gains, cults. These are cultures of meaning that use the pillars and give people something to live and die for.",
    "uid": "48748a328b27aebf",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 613.42,
    "end": 621.42
  },
  {
    "text": "But that's exactly why we, as a society, must offer better alternatives.",
    "uid": "a3860a45da941324",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 622.42,
    "end": 626.42
  },
  {
    "text": "We need to build these pillars within our families and our institutions to help people become their best selves.",
    "uid": "935862c77e00b185",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 627.42,
    "end": 632.42
  },
  {
    "text": "But living a meaningful life takes work. It's an ongoing process.",
    "uid": "7c5f4e3d5f8714cd",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 634.42,
    "end": 638.42
  },
  {
    "text": "As each day goes by, we're constantly creating our lives, adding to our story.",
    "uid": "8bfe54a59f84841c",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 638.42,
    "end": 643.42
  },
  {
    "text": "And sometimes we can get off track.",
    "uid": "a299a6f45a73a729",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 644.42,
    "end": 647.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Whenever that happens to me, I remember a powerful experience I had with my father.",
    "uid": "5470ae6daa860f82",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 648.42,
    "end": 653.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Several months after I graduated from college, my dad had a massive heart attack that should have killed him.",
    "uid": "66aa30f265fa12ef",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 656.18,
    "end": 662.18
  },
  {
    "text": "He survived and when I asked him what was going through his mind as he faced that,",
    "uid": "2c73a6af7a5f4fac",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 663.18,
    "end": 667.18
  },
  {
    "text": "he said all he could think about was needing to live so he could be there for my brother and me.",
    "uid": "2cae20be399b0ce1",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 667.18,
    "end": 672.18
  },
  {
    "text": "And this gave him the will to fight for life.",
    "uid": "5f5da4e3e8cd8119",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 673.18,
    "end": 675.18
  },
  {
    "text": "When he went under anesthesia for emergency surgery, instead of counting backwards from ten, he repeated our names like a mantra.",
    "uid": "76dfdb687f88e806",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 676.18,
    "end": 684.18
  },
  {
    "text": "He wanted our names to be the last words he spoke on earth if he died.",
    "uid": "30e796e3a609cec9",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 685.18,
    "end": 690.18
  },
  {
    "text": "My dad is a carpenter and a sufi.",
    "uid": "9700bdf7148f4203",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 692.98,
    "end": 695.98
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a humble life but a good life.",
    "uid": "811c23a2f5098e3e",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 696.98,
    "end": 699.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Lying there facing death, he had a reason to live.",
    "uid": "ab873939c1388356",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 700.98,
    "end": 703.98
  },
  {
    "text": "His sense of belonging with an his family, his purpose as a dad, his transcendent meditation repeating our names.",
    "uid": "20cd35a332e3b0a9",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 706.98,
    "end": 712.98
  },
  {
    "text": "These he says are the reasons why he survived. That's the story he tells himself.",
    "uid": "3217f32c34b21ce6",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 713.98,
    "end": 717.98
  },
  {
    "text": "That's the power of meaning.",
    "uid": "f299f10ec7cdab84",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 719.98,
    "end": 721.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Happiness comes and goes.",
    "uid": "e99a376ed0e389d2",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 722.98,
    "end": 724.98
  },
  {
    "text": "But when life is really good and when things are really bad, having meaning gives you something to hold on to.",
    "uid": "f9ccc4acb43fbf9f",
    "source": "TED - There_s_more_to_life_than_being_happy_Emily_Esfahani_Smith_TED",
    "start": 725.98,
    "end": 731.98
  }
]